========= 8.0.0.029 (beta-pre-dashboard-testing) =========

add(internal-http): Add documentation mode which disables all core features.
add(widgets/alerts): Add setPlayback option to enable/disable playback functionality.
update(widgets/global): setThemeType default is now "primary"
update(widgets/streams): Ability to set stream as muted.
update(widgets/js): `setAnimationStartDuration` now impacts `setBackgroundAnimated` animation time. (Default 1.5 seconds)
update(widgets/utils): Improve error handling in element animation functions
feat(widget styles, utils): update widget container positioning and enhance string processing logic
feat(config): update allowedHosts for documentation server
feat(config): update event and source configurations for improved functionality and documentation
feat(docs): enhance documentation for events, sources, and widgets; update last modified dates
feat(portal): add meta tags for improved SEO and social sharing
feat(index): enhance Cron job functionality by adding cache data fetching and spotter updating
fix(utility): adjust webhook rate limit from 3 to 2 for improved control
fix(widgets/strings): Fix string manipulation issues in various widget components
fix(internal-parser): Make sure merging actually merges...
fix(config): Fix sfx direct files for Tornado Warnings. 
fix(widget/polywarn): adjust styling and functionality for better user experience
fix(widget/stream): adjust styling and functionality for better user experience
fix(parsing): add optional chaining to conditions parsing for safety
fix(utils): change notification text element from paragraph to span for better styling
fix(widget/strings): correct coordinate object structure for distance calculations
fix(widgets/streams): adjust widget padding and refresh time settings
fix(widgets/streams): auto-reconnect by error. (err-check)
refactor(probability): consolidate probability settings and update parsing logic

